body:
Champion idea #1
Name: Titerous, the dark Crusader
Abilities: 
Passive: Juggernaut &ndash; 
Titerous is strengthened by his broad strength and solid defence &ndash; 
Titerous gains 10 health points via every 1 armour and magic resist points. Making him a general threat to all who oppose him.
Q. Shield wall &ndash;
Active: Titerous dashes forward which if he hits a target he deals physical damage and slight knocking a single target backwards wile marking the target with a Black cross shortly after Titerous will block/parry the next ability/auto attack from the marked champion/monster.
W. strengthened will -
Passive: Titerous gains bonus armour and magic resist around enemy champions.
Active: Titerous gains massive armour and magic resist at the cost of reduction of his own damage.
E. Swing of the ages &ndash; 
Active: Titerous takes a slight delay which he lines up his mace to take a massive swing knocking the target sideways, which does damage based on a percentage of the targets max health. In the doing so if the target collides with any nearby terrain the target will be stunned for 1 second.
R. Bring down the gates &ndash;
Active: Titerous takes a second to charge up his gigantic mace and slams it into the ground which creates a massive earthquake slowing the targets struck by the ability, which does moderate damage and reduces the champions armour and magic resist for 5 seconds while marking the champions hit by the ability for 5 seconds revealing them on the map. (Titerous can also use this ability on structures)  i decided to come up with this champion idea because i use to love playign taric and leona but i thought of making a champion that is simalir to these champions bu could actualy do damage. so yeah help me make this champion!!!
